msgid "Right-Click on Hikaru to see How to Play Guide."
msgstr "Haz clic derecho sobre Hikaru para ver la guía de cómo jugar."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:293
msgid ""
"Ah, just another usual day of being the village militia. I wish something "
"extraordinary happened once."
msgstr ""
"Ah, solo otro día normal siendo la milicia del pueblo. Ojalá ocurriera algo "
"extraordinario alguna vez."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:295
msgid ""
"I grew up reading so much about the great heroes of our people that I really "
"want my own sort of adventure. An adventure of the like Ryuuma had before he "
"became the war hero of the Great War."
msgstr ""
"Crecí leyendo tanto sobre los grandes héroes de nuestro pueblo que realmente "
"quiero tener mi propia aventura, del tipo que tuvo Ryuuma antes de "
"convertirse en el héroe de la Gran Guerra."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:297
msgid "Be careful what you wish for."
msgstr "Ten cuidado con lo que deseas."

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:305
msgid ""
"Hikaru, you forget that Ryuuma of Shimotsuki made his mark during the great "
"war at the southern borders. After the war ended, there have not been any "
"major happenings."
msgstr ""
"Hikaru, olvidas que Ryuuma de Shimotsuki dejó su huella durante la gran "
"guerra en las fronteras del sur. Desde que terminó la guerra no ha pasado "
"nada importante."

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:310
msgid "Hey, look! There is movement near the ruins!"
msgstr "¡Oye, mira! ¡Hay movimiento cerca de las ruinas!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:312
msgid "That's where we keep the..."
msgstr "¡Ahí es donde guardamos la…!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Cendrillon
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:314
msgid "Looks like the Lady was correct! I sense it here!"
msgstr "¡Parece que la señora tenía razón! ¡La siento aquí!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Cendrillon
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:316
msgid "There it is!"
msgstr "¡Ahí está!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:325
msgid "Hey, wait! You there! What are you doing?"
msgstr "¡Oye, espera! ¡Tú ahí! ¿Qué están haciendo?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Cendrillon
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:327
msgid ""
"It does not matter. We have what we need. You go on ahead. I shall delay "
"them a bit and join up with you!"
msgstr ""
"No importa. Ya tenemos lo que necesitamos. Tú sigue adelante. Yo los "
"retrasaré un poco y luego me reúno contigo."

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:340
msgid "Hikaru, they have taken the Electrifyre!"
msgstr "¡Hikaru, se llevaron la Electryfire!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:342
msgid ""
"That relic has been under the protection of our village since time "
"immemorial! We must retrieve it at all costs!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esa reliquia ha estado bajo la protección de nuestro pueblo desde tiempos "
"inmemoriales! ¡Tenemos que recuperarla a toda costa!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:344
msgid "Quick! Rally to me and we shall engage this enemy!"
msgstr "¡Rápido! ¡Reúnanse conmigo y enfrentemos a este enemigo!"

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:346
msgid ""
"The <span color='#FFA756'><i>Unstable Elementals</i></span> units will "
"switch forms based on the terrain they are on. Use this knowledge to expose "
"their weakest form. The <span color='#FFA756'><i>Fire Guardian</i></span> "
"units might be slightly stronger than usually encountered. The <span "
"color='#FFA756'><i>Ice Ghosts</i></span> can inflict slow and are fast. The "
"<span color='#FFA756'><i>Giant Mudcrawlers</i></span> and <span "
"color='#FFA756'><i>Mudcrawlers</i></span> can be easily overwhelmed by "
"bladed or piercing attacks, just do not let them attack you in packs. Try to "
"restrict their movement by exploiting the Zone of Control (ZoC). It is "
"advisable to confront them in groups of two of three units and in locations "
"where the enemy units cannot benefit from. Good Luck."
msgstr ""
"Las unidades <span color='#FFA756'><i>elementales inestables</i></span> "
"cambian de forma según el terreno en que estén. Usa ese conocimiento para "
"exponer su forma más débil. Las unidades <span color='#FFA756'><i>guardianes "
"de fuego</i></span> pueden ser un poco más fuertes de lo habitual. Los <span "
"color='#FFA756'><i>fantasmas de hielo</i></span> pueden ralentizar y son "
"rápidos. A los <span color='#FFA756'><i>reptadores de barro gigantes</i></"
"span> y <span color='#FFA756'><i>reptadores de barro</i></span> se los puede "
"vencer fácilmente con ataques cortantes o perforantes, pero no los dejes "
"atacarte en grupo. Intenta limitar su movimiento usando zonas de control "
"(ZoC). Lo recomendable es enfrentarlos en grupos de dos o tres unidades y en "
"lugares donde el enemigo no se beneficie del terreno. ¡Buena suerte!"

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:348
msgid ""
"When encountering new enemy units, it is always worthwhile to check the unit "
"on the sidebar UI. You might see some new traits or abilities not seen "
"before and this data can guide you in formulating your strategy more "
"effectively."
msgstr ""
"Cuando te enfrentes a unidades enemigas nuevas, siempre vale la pena "
"revisarlas en la barra lateral. Puede que veas rasgos o habilidades que no "
"habías visto antes y esa información te ayudará a planear mejor tu "
"estrategia."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:355
msgid "Where were the guards that have been stationed there for the night?"
msgstr "¿Dónde estaban los guardias que dejamos de turno esta noche?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Cendrillon
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:357
msgid "Oh, those two? They got in the way. We took care of them."
msgstr "Ah, ¿esos dos? Estorbaron. Nos encargamos de ellos."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:359
msgid "I shall make you regret doing that!"
msgstr "¡Te haré arrepentirte de haber hecho eso!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:367
msgid ""
"Send a scout to the Perch! We shall require the aid of the Eagle Riders in "
"catching the robbers!"
msgstr ""
"¡Envíen un explorador al Percha! ¡Necesitaremos la ayuda de los jinetes de "
"águila para atrapar a los ladrones!"

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:385
msgid "There are some wild ogres near by!"
msgstr "¡Hay ogros salvajes cerca!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:392
msgid ""
"Do not enrage them. I think it's better if we let the enemy agitate them "
"first."
msgstr ""
"No los enfurezcamos. Creo que es mejor dejar que el enemigo los provoque "
"primero."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:394
msgid ""
"They seem to be approaching the enemy from their den. This might work in our "
"favor."
msgstr ""
"Parece que se acercan al enemigo desde su guarida. Esto podría jugar a "
"nuestro favor."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:407
msgid ""
"<i>Aragwaith Adepts</i> have a strong magical ranged attack and can heal "
"your units. The number of adepts available to you right now is limited and "
"hence, you should try your best to keep them alive in this scenario."
msgstr ""
"Las <i>Adeptas Aragwaithi</i> tienen un potente ataque mágico a distancia y "
"pueden sanar a tus unidades. Ahora mismo el número de adeptas es limitado, "
"así que haz todo lo posible por mantenerlas vivas en este escenario."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:419
msgid ""
"Hikaru is a <i>Longswordsman</i> and as such, he has superior offense "
"capabilities and moderate defences. It is best to utilize him to damage "
"enemy units enough for other lower level units to land the killing blow and "
"get the experience."
msgstr ""
"Hikaru es un <i>Espadachín Largo</i> y por eso tiene gran capacidad ofensiva "
"y defensas moderadas. Lo mejor es usarlo para dañar lo suficiente a las "
"unidades enemigas y que unidades de nivel más bajo den el golpe final y "
"ganen experiencia."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:431
msgid ""
"Archers are cheap to recruit, so you can have a lot of them. They are good "
"at shooting from far away, and you can make them even better by upgrading "
"them later."
msgstr ""
"Los Arqueros son baratos de reclutar, así que puedes tener muchos. Son "
"buenos disparando desde lejos y los puedes hacer aún mejores al subirlos de "
"nivel."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:443
msgid ""
"The Spearman is strong in attack and decent in defense, so keep about 1-2 "
"Spearmen to protect important areas. Spearmen can become leaders, making "
"them even more valuable later."
msgstr ""
"El Lancero es fuerte en ataque y decente en defensa, así que mantén 1 o 2 "
"protegiendo zonas importantes. Los lanceros pueden convertirse en líderes, "
"lo que los hace aún más valiosos después."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:455
msgid ""
"Swordsmen excel in close combat against enemies vulnerable to their slashing "
"attacks. Use them strategically in smaller numbers to take advantage of this "
"strength. Their upgrades offer specialized options to enhance either their "
"survival or damage output."
msgstr ""
"Los Espadachines destacan en combate cuerpo a cuerpo contra enemigos débiles "
"al daño cortante. Úsalos estratégicamente en menor número para aprovechar "
"esa ventaja. Sus mejoras son especializadas: algunas aumentan la "
"supervivencia y otras el daño."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:467
msgid ""
"Scouts are faster than Spearmen but weaker than Eagle riders. Use them to "
"quickly deal piercing damage in situations where you need it right away."
msgstr ""
"Los Exploradores son más rápidos que los lanceros, pero más débiles que los "
"jinetes de águila. Úsalos para infligir daño perforante rápido cuando lo "
"necesites de inmediato."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=unit
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:510
msgid "It's a fire elemental!"
msgstr "¡Es un elemental de fuego!"

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:512
msgid ""
"<i>Fire Guardians</i> have decent melee and ranged attacks. Thus, it is an "
"optimal tactic to strike them first and strike them hard."
msgstr ""
"Los <i>Guardianes de fuego</i> tienen ataques cuerpo a cuerpo y a distancia "
"decentes. Por eso, la táctica ideal es golpearlos primero y golpear fuerte."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=unit
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:526
msgid "Woah, it's an ice ghost!"
msgstr "¡Vaya, es un fantasma de hielo!"

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:528
msgid ""
"<i>Ice Ghosts</i> prefer to inflict <i>slow</i> on your units and let the "
"other units deal with your slowed units afterwards. It is recommended to "
"attack them with the ranged attack of <i>Aragwaith Adepts</i> and then "
"finish them off with either a Spearman, a Scout or a Swordsman."
msgstr ""
"Los <i>Fantasmas de hielo</i> prefieren ralentizar a tus unidades y dejar "
"que el resto las remate. Se recomienda atacarlos primero con el ataque a "
"distancia de las <i>adeptas aragwaithi</i> y luego terminarlos con un "
"lancero, un explorador o un espadachín."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=unit
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:545
msgid "It's a mud elemental!"
msgstr "¡Es un elemental de barro!"

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:547
msgid ""
"<i>Mudcrawlers</i> and their giant variants are weak elementals created from "
"earth. They prefer sticking together in packs. An Aragwaith Adept can "
"incinerate them with ease."
msgstr ""
"Los <i>Reptadores de barro</i> y sus variantes gigantes son elementales "
"débiles hechos de tierra. Prefieren andar en manada. Una adepta aragwaith "
"puede incinerarlos sin problema."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:563
msgid "We lost someone!"
msgstr "¡Perdimos a alguien!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:565
msgid ""
"Stick together and do not let them surround you! Focus your attacks and take "
"them out swiftly."
msgstr ""
"¡Manténganse juntos y no dejen que los rodeen! ¡Concentren los ataques y "
"elimínenlos rápido!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=unit
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:576
msgid "Ouch! I underestimated you lot..."
msgstr "¡Auch! Los subestimé…"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:578
msgid "Where are you taking the relic?!"
msgstr "¡¿A dónde llevan la reliquia?!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Cendrillon
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:580
msgid "Our fortress... South... Further South..."
msgstr "Nuestra fortaleza… al sur… más al sur…"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:590
msgid "He died from his wounds..."
msgstr "Murió por sus heridas…"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:592
msgid ""
"He mentioned a fortress further south from here. That must where they are "
"heading with the sword."
msgstr ""
"Mencionó una fortaleza más al sur. Ahí deben estar llevándose la espada."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:595
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:655
msgid "What should we do? Should we send a scout to Astya?"
msgstr "¿Qué hacemos? ¿Enviamos un explorador a Astya?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:597
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:657
msgid ""
"That would not do us any good. Too much time would have passed by the time "
"they arrive. The sword and the mages will have gone with the winds by then."
msgstr ""
"Eso no serviría de nada. Cuando llegaran ya habría pasado demasiado tiempo. "
"La espada y los magos se habrían ido hace rato."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:599
msgid ""
"Many of us have not even left the outskirts of the village. Can we really "
"bring it back?"
msgstr ""
"Muchos de nosotros ni siquiera hemos salido de las afueras del pueblo. ¿De "
"verdad podemos recuperarla?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:602
msgid ""
"Do you remember the stories of Ryuuma the Hero? Would he back down from this "
"if he was here?"
msgstr ""
"¿Recuerdan las historias de Ryuuma el héroe? ¿Él se rendiría ante esto si "
"estuviera aquí?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:604
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:663
msgid ""
"No, he would not. The sword belongs to the village, we have to get it back."
msgstr ""
"No, no lo haría. La espada pertenece al pueblo, tenemos que recuperarla."

#. [event], NARRATOR_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:606
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:665
msgid "<b><i>Cheers of determination resonated through the Aragwaithi!</i></b>"
msgstr "<b><i>¡Gritos de determinación resonaron entre los Aragwaithi!</i></b>"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:608
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:667
msgid "It's decided then. Assemble a raiding party! We are going South."
msgstr "Entonces está decidido. ¡Formen un grupo de asalto! ¡Vamos al sur!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Cendrillon
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:640
msgid "Haha! Time to go!"
msgstr "¡Ja ja! ¡Hora de irse!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:652
msgid "Oh, no! He escaped!"
msgstr "¡Oh, no! ¡Se escapó!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:659
msgid ""
"Before he started attacking us, one of his underlings made off with the "
"sword. They were dashing southwards."
msgstr ""
"Antes de que empezara a atacarnos, uno de sus subordinados se llevó la "
"espada. Iban corriendo hacia el sur."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/01_A_Village_Robbed.cfg:661
msgid "That's the only clue we have. I suggest we go south."
msgstr "Esa es la única pista que tenemos. Sugiero que vayamos al sur."

#. [scenario], id=02_Wild_Knolls
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:5
msgid "Wild Knolls"
msgstr "Colinas salvajes"

#. [side], type=Aragwaith Enchantress
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:63
msgid "Ayanami"
msgstr "Ayanami"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:224
msgid "Save Ayanami from the vicious insects"
msgstr "Salvar a Ayanami de los insectos feroces"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:232
msgid "Find all the scattered pages"
msgstr "Encontrar todas las páginas dispersas"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:241
msgid "Death of Ayanami"
msgstr "Muerte de Ayanami"

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:254
msgid "Use Scouts to rush ahead and help your ally."
msgstr "Usa exploradores para avanzar rápido y ayudar a tu aliada."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:260
msgid "Avoid recruiting/recalling too many Scouts."
msgstr "Evita reincorporar o reclutar demasiados exploradores."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:266
msgid "Use Spearmen as shields to withstand the enemy attacks."
msgstr "Usa lanceros como escudos para resistir los ataques enemigos."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:269
msgid "Use Archers against enemies with no ranged attack."
msgstr "Usa arqueros contra enemigos sin ataque a distancia."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:272
msgid "Use Adepts to heal injured units."
msgstr "Usa adeptas para sanar a las unidades heridas."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:277
msgid "Confront the caves in groups of three-four units."
msgstr "Enfrenta las cuevas en grupos de tres o cuatro unidades."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:283
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:188
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:487
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:326
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:211
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:316
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/08A_Enemy_of_My_Enemy.cfg:428
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/09A_Bastion_of_the_Forgotten.cfg:365
msgid "Recall costs are a fraction of the recruit cost."
msgstr "El costo de reincorporar es una fracción del costo de reclutar."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:287
msgid "Have around 42 gold left over while saving the allied leader."
msgstr "Deja aproximadamente 42 de oro mientras salvas a la líder aliada."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:464
msgid "The mages must have gone through here."
msgstr "Los magos deben haber pasado por aquí."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:466
msgid ""
"There are a lot of wild beasts here. We should be careful while we advance."
msgstr "Hay muchas bestias salvajes aquí. Debemos tener cuidado al avanzar."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ayanami
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:468
msgid "Fellow Aragwaithi, please help us!"
msgstr "¡Hermanos Aragwaithi, por favor ayúdennos!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:470
msgid "They seem to be under attack!"
msgstr "¡Parece que están siendo atacados!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:472
msgid ""
"Hikaru, send in some scouts first to keep the ants busy. Infantry won't "
"reach them in time."
msgstr ""
"Hikaru, envía primero a algunos exploradores para mantener ocupadas a las "
"hormigas. La infantería no llegará a tiempo."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:474
msgid ""
"Quick, scouts! Ready your spears and rush ahead! We shall catch when we can!"
msgstr ""
"¡Rápido, exploradores! ¡Preparen sus lanzas y avancen! ¡Los alcanzaremos "
"cuando podamos!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=veteran_scout
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:478
msgid "Let's go!"
msgstr "¡Vamos!"

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:481
msgid ""
"In this scenario stage, your ally needs immediate assistance from you but is "
"far away. Your infantry type units cannot reach them on time. In this case, "
"you should intially recall scouts and send them in first to delay and harass "
"the wolves, allowing time for your infantry to arrive and finish them off."
msgstr ""
"En esta parte del escenario, tu aliada necesita ayuda inmediata pero está "
"lejos. Tus unidades de infantería no llegarán a tiempo. En este caso, debes "
"reincorporar exploradores y enviarlos primero para retrasar y molestar a los "
"enemigos, dando tiempo a que llegue la infantería y los remate."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ayanami
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:495
msgid "Thank you so much, friends! We are grateful for the rescue!"
msgstr "¡Muchas gracias, amigos! ¡Estamos muy agradecidos por el rescate!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ayanami
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:580
msgid "My name is Ayanami and I am a researcher at the city of Aeranas."
msgstr "Me llamo Ayanami y soy investigadora en la ciudad de Aeranas."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:582
msgid "The far Northern city? You seem to be a long way from home."
msgstr "¿La ciudad del lejano norte? Estás muy lejos de casa."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ayanami
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:584
msgid ""
"Yes, I am. I am currently on an expedition to search for some lost magic "
"material from ancient times. I have ascertained that they are here somewhere."
msgstr ""
"Sí, así es. Estoy en una expedición buscando materiales mágicos perdidos de "
"la antigüedad. He confirmado que están por aquí, en algún lugar."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:586
msgid ""
"We are currently on a quest as well. Our village heirloom has been stolen "
"and we must reclaim it."
msgstr ""
"Nosotros también estamos en una misión. Nos robaron la reliquia del pueblo y "
"tenemos que recuperarla."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ayanami
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:588
msgid ""
"A theft? That sounds terrible. If I can finish my task here, I suppose I can "
"lend my aid."
msgstr ""
"¿Un robo? Eso suena horrible. Si termino mi tarea aquí, supongo que puedo "
"ayudarlos."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:590
msgid "What are you looking for?"
msgstr "¿Qué estás buscando?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ayanami
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:592
msgid ""
"There are three magically protected pages somewhere here. I am looking for "
"them."
msgstr "Hay tres páginas protegidas mágicamente por aquí. Las estoy buscando."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:594
msgid ""
"That should not take very long. If we work together, we can find them in no "
"time!"
msgstr ""
"No debería tomar mucho tiempo. ¡Si trabajamos juntos, las encontraremos en "
"un instante!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ayanami
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:596
msgid "I will let you have some of my adepts for this search."
msgstr "Te dejaré algunas de mis adeptas para la búsqueda."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:598
msgid "You can now recruit <b><i>Aragwaith Adepts</i></b>!"
msgstr "¡Ahora puedes reclutar <b><i>Adeptas Aragwaithi</i></b>!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=unit
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:628
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:659
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:690
msgid "Hey, I found one of the pages!"
msgstr "¡Oye, encontré una de las páginas!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ayanami
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:630
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:661
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:692
msgid "Excellent!"
msgstr "¡Excelente!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ayanami
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:711
msgid "Thank you all so much for helping in this endeavour!"
msgstr "¡Muchas gracias a todos por ayudar en esta tarea!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:713
msgid "You are welcome. We always help people in need of it."
msgstr "De nada. Siempre ayudamos a quien lo necesita."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ayanami
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:715
msgid "I wish you all the best in your coming battles and adventures."
msgstr "Les deseo lo mejor en las batallas y aventuras que vienen."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:717
msgid "Thank you, Lady Ayanami!"
msgstr "¡Gracias, señora Ayanami!"

#. [then], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Eikichi
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:725
msgid ""
"Allow me to join you in your quest, friends. You have rescued me from "
"certain death and I must return the favor."
msgstr ""
"Permítanme unirme a su misión, amigos. Me salvaron de una muerte segura y "
"debo devolverles el favor."

#. [then], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:727
msgid ""
"Welcome, Eikichi! Your archery expertise shall be invaluable to our quest!"
msgstr ""
"¡Bienvenido, Eikichi! ¡Tu habilidad con el arco será invaluable en nuestra "
"misión!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=unit
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:755
msgid "Looks like this is the end for me!"
msgstr "¡Parece que este es mi fin!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:757
msgid "How did we let her die? She could have given us some adepts!"
msgstr "¿Cómo dejamos que muriera? ¡Nos podría haber dado algunas adeptas!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:779
msgid "She was a vicious foe!"
msgstr "¡Era una enemiga feroz!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:798
msgid ""
"It is sad we had to eliminate them. They were simply guarding their homes..."
msgstr ""
"Es triste que tuviéramos que eliminarlas. Solo estaban defendiendo su hogar…"

#. [+unit]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:827
msgid "Aelynthi"
msgstr "Aelynthi"

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Aelynthi
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:854
msgid "Oh, hello."
msgstr "Oh, hola."

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:856
msgid "Are you a faerie?"
msgstr "¿Eres un hada?"

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Aelynthi
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:858
msgid "Yes, I am. This is my home."
msgstr "Sí, lo soy. Este es mi hogar."

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:860
msgid "Would you like help us out?"
msgstr "¿Te gustaría ayudarnos?"

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Aelynthi
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:862
msgid "No, I don't think I will. I have things to do here."
msgstr "No, creo que no. Tengo cosas que hacer aquí."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Aelynthi
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:879
msgid "I am going back to my hut!"
msgstr "¡Me regreso a mi choza!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=unit
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:906
msgid "Hey, I see someone! He's barely alive! Come, quick!"
msgstr "¡Oye, veo a alguien! ¡Apenas está vivo! ¡Vengan rápido!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Eikichi
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:930
msgid "Thank you...for saving...me..."
msgstr "Gracias… por salvarme…"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:932
msgid "Rest now. We can talk after you have healed up."
msgstr "Descansa ahora. Hablaremos cuando te hayas recuperado."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:935
msgid ""
"This loyal unit is injured and should be placed next to a healer or in a "
"village to receive healing."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad leal está herida y debe colocarse junto a un sanador o en un "
"pueblo para recibir curación."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/02_Wild_Knolls.cfg:950
msgid ""
"We have delayed far too long here! I fear we already lost the chance to "
"reclaim the heirloom."
msgstr ""
"¡Nos hemos demorado demasiado aquí! Me temo que ya perdimos la oportunidad "
"de recuperar la reliquia."

#. [scenario], id=03_Southern_Sojourn
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:6
msgid "Southern Sojourn"
msgstr "Estancia sureña"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:151
msgid "Reach the southern edge of the map with Hikaru"
msgstr "Llegar al borde sur del mapa con Hikaru"

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:167
msgid "Engage the isolated enemy units in groups of 2 or 3 units."
msgstr "Enfrenta a las unidades enemigas aisladas en grupos de 2 o 3."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:170
msgid "Use Eagle Riders to rush ahead and flank retreating enemies."
msgstr ""
"Usa jinetes de águila para avanzar rápido y flanquear a los enemigos que se "
"retiran."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:180
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:482
msgid "Try to level up a Swordsman into a Guard."
msgstr "Intenta subir de nivel a un espadachín hasta guardia."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:183
msgid "Attack during the day, defend during the night."
msgstr "Ataca de día, defiende de noche."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=veteran_scout
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:260
msgid "Hikaru, we have now entered vampire lands!"
msgstr "¡Hikaru, ya entramos en tierras de vampiros!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:262
msgid ""
"I would prefer to avoid a confrontation with them for as long as possible. "
"Exhausting our forces before we even get near the fortress would not bode "
"well for us."
msgstr ""
"Prefiero evitar un enfrentamiento con ellos todo el tiempo que sea posible. "
"Agotar nuestras fuerzas antes de llegar cerca de la fortaleza no sería bueno "
"para nosotros."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:264
msgid "I advise caution. There are vampires ahead!"
msgstr "Recomiendo precaución. ¡Hay vampiros adelante!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=vampire_leader
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:266
msgid ""
"Ah, Aragwaithi. Those mages and dwarves told us you would be showing up. "
"Turn back now."
msgstr ""
"Ah, Aragwaithi. Esos magos y enanos nos dijeron que aparecerían. Den la "
"vuelta ahora."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:268
msgid ""
"We are looking for some magicians carrying an artifact. Did they pass "
"through here?"
msgstr "Buscamos a unos magos que llevan un artefacto. ¿Pasaron por aquí?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=vampire_leader
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:270
msgid ""
"They have passed through here three days ago. They have also paid us a lot "
"of gold and blood potions just to bar you passage."
msgstr ""
"Pasaron por aquí hace tres días. También nos pagaron mucho oro y pociones de "
"sangre solo para impedirles el paso."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:272
msgid ""
"Would you allow us passage as well, lady vampire? We do not have much gold "
"but we can give you whatever we have."
msgstr ""
"¿Nos dejarías pasar también, señora vampiro? No tenemos mucho oro, pero "
"podemos darte lo que tengamos."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:274
msgid "Soryu!"
msgstr "¡Soryu!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=veteran_scout
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:276
msgid "I don't think that will work..."
msgstr "No creo que eso funcione…"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=vampire_leader
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:278
msgid "No. We shall fight you if you enter our lands."
msgstr "No. Los combatiremos si entran en nuestras tierras."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=vampire_leader
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:280
msgid "Minions, kill them and harvest their blood!"
msgstr "¡Esbirros, mátenlos y cosechen su sangre!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=veteran_scout
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:282
msgid "Lead us to battle, Hikaru!"
msgstr "¡Líderanos a la batalla, Hikaru!"

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:289
msgid ""
"Vampires are <i>chaotic</i> with the exception of some having the "
"<i>neutral</i> alignment. It is better to defend during the night time and "
"then retaliate during the day. Do note that the objective is not fighting "
"and defeating the vampires. You should focus on moving your leader to the "
"southern map edge."
msgstr ""
"Los vampiros son <i>caóticos</i>, salvo algunos que tienen alineación "
"<i>neutral</i>. Es mejor defender de noche y contraatacar de día. Recuerda "
"que el objetivo no es pelear ni derrotar a los vampiros. Debes concentrarte "
"en llevar a tu líder al borde sur del mapa."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:291
msgid ""
"Same vampire units are more attack oriented than others so you should focus "
"on taking down any <i>Blood Apprentices</i> or <i>Blood Hulks</i> if you get "
"the opportunity."
msgstr ""
"Algunas unidades vampiro son más ofensivas que otras, así que enfócate en "
"eliminar cualquier <i>aprendiz de sangre</i> o <i>coloso de sangre</i> si "
"tienes la oportunidad."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=eagle_rider1
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:323
msgid ""
"We have received your message! We are here to help! Let's get that relic "
"back!"
msgstr "¡Recibimos tu mensaje! ¡Vinimos a ayudar! ¡Recuperemos esa reliquia!"

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:330
msgid ""
"You can recruit the <i><b>Aragwaith Eagle Riders</b></i> now. These units "
"are capable of moving fast and mostly serve the role of scouts. They have a "
"<i>blade</i> attack as well as an <i>impact</i> attack that is only usable "
"during attacking. Utilize the high mobility and attacking power of these "
"units to flank isolated enemy units and disallow them to retreat."
msgstr ""
"Ahora puedes reclutar <i><b>Jinetes de Águila Aragwaithi</b></i>. Estas "
"unidades se mueven rápido y sirven principalmente como exploradores. Tienen "
"ataque <i>cortante</i> y un ataque <i>de impacto</i> que solo se usa al "
"atacar. Aprovecha su alta movilidad y poder de ataque para flanquear "
"unidades enemigas aisladas e impedir que se retiren."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:344
msgid ""
"Going further south will lead us deeper into vampire lands. I hope we can "
"find the fortress soon and retrieve the sword."
msgstr ""
"Ir más al sur nos llevará más profundo en tierras de vampiros. Espero que "
"encontremos pronto la fortaleza y recuperemos la espada."

#. [event], NAMED_LOYAL_UNIT
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:384
msgid "Pyrah"
msgstr "Pyrah"

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Pyrah
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:398
msgid "<i>(yawns)</i> Hey, what's the big deal? I was napping!"
msgstr "<i>(bosteza)</i> Oye, ¿qué pasa? ¡Estaba durmiendo la siesta!"

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=unit
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:400
msgid ""
"Oops, did not mean to interupt. What are you doing in the middle of vampire "
"lands anyways?"
msgstr ""
"Ups, no quería interrumpir. ¿Qué hacen en medio de tierras de vampiros, por "
"cierto?"

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Pyrah
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:402
msgid "I am journeying southwards to meet my elder sister."
msgstr "Estoy viajando al sur para encontrarme con mi hermana mayor."

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:404
msgid ""
"You have a lot of luck to have avoided vampires so long despite being so "
"near their castle."
msgstr ""
"Tienes mucha suerte de haber evitado a los vampiros tanto tiempo estando tan "
"cerca de su castillo."

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Pyrah
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:406
msgid ""
"What are you aragwaithi doing here? Should not you all be in the northern "
"kingdoms?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué hacen unos aragwaithi aquí? ¿No deberían estar todos en los reinos del "
"norte?"

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:408
msgid "We are going south to retrieve something that was stolen from us."
msgstr "Vamos al sur a recuperar algo que nos robaron."

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Pyrah
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:410
msgid ""
"We share a common path. May I join you in your journey south until I can "
"meet up with my sister?"
msgstr ""
"Compartimos camino. ¿Puedo unirme a su viaje al sur hasta que encuentre a mi "
"hermana?"

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:412
msgid "I suppose we can. The more the merrier."
msgstr "Supongo que sí. Cuantos más, mejor."

#. [+unit], NARRATOR_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:414
msgid "Pyrah the <i>Faerie Sprite</i> has joined you!"
msgstr "¡Pyrah la <i>duende hada</i> se ha unido a ti!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=vampire_leader
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:433
msgid ""
"Curses on you, aragwaith! You may have defeated me, but the other vampire "
"lords will take care of you soon enough."
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos sean, aragwaith! Puede que me hayan derrotado, pero los otros "
"señores vampiro se encargarán de ustedes pronto."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=vampire_leader
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:435
msgid "Do not think that you can tread on vampire lands and pass unscatched."
msgstr "No crean que pueden pisar tierras vampiro y salir ilesos."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Pyrah
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:446
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:704
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:992
msgid "I should have stayed in my tree..."
msgstr "Debería haberme quedado en mi árbol…"

#. [event], NARRATOR_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:459
msgid "<i>A loud rumbling noise is heard echoing the nearby woods...</i>"
msgstr "<i>Se escucha un fuerte ruido retumbar en los bosques cercanos…</i>"

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Oakent
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:471
msgid "<i>(belowing)</i> Why have you woken me?"
msgstr "<i>(bramando)</i> ¿Por qué me despertaron?"

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:473
msgid ""
"Oops! Sorry, we did not mean to disturb your slumber, mighty Wose. We were "
"just passing through."
msgstr ""
"¡Ups! Perdón, no quisimos molestar tu sueño, poderoso wose. Solo estábamos "
"pasando."

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Oakent
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:475
msgid ""
"You are Aragwaithi. I remember the past well. Your people had helped our "
"people against the dark one eons ago. Tell me, friend, how can this old one "
"be of service?"
msgstr ""
"Ustedes son Aragwaithi. Recuerdo bien el pasado. Su pueblo ayudó al nuestro "
"contra el oscuro hace eones. Dime, amigo, ¿cómo puede este viejo servirles?"

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:477
msgid ""
"We are trying to rush through these lands to recover something which has "
"been taken from us. Would you you be able to offer any kind of assistance?"
msgstr ""
"Estamos intentando atravesar rápido estas tierras para recuperar algo que "
"nos quitaron. ¿Podrías ofrecernos algún tipo de ayuda?"

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Oakent
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:479
msgid "Perhaps. Let me awaken the other woses who are slumbering nearby..."
msgstr "Tal vez. Déjame despertar a los otros woses que duermen cerca…"

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:498
msgid ""
"Hikaru, let us use this opportunity and go across this place as swiftly as "
"possible!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hikaru, aprovechemos esta oportunidad y crucemos este lugar lo más rápido "
"posible!"

#. [+unit], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:500
msgid "Right."
msgstr "De acuerdo."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/03_Southern_Sojourn.cfg:512
msgid "I see more vampires arriving! We are heavily outnumbered!"
msgstr "¡Veo llegar más vampiros! ¡Estamos en gran desventaja numérica!"

#. [scenario], id=04_Fogbound_Valley
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:6
msgid "Fogbound Valley"
msgstr "Valle envuelto en niebla"

#. [side]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:435
msgid "Ancient Stones"
msgstr "Piedras ancestrales"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:455
msgid "Survive until the end of turns"
msgstr "Sobrevivir hasta el final de los turnos"

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:473
msgid "Aragwaithi have the terrain advantage on this map."
msgstr "Los Aragwaithi tienen ventaja de terreno en este mapa."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:476
msgid "Utilize Healing to sustain your units."
msgstr "Utiliza la sanación para mantener a tus unidades."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:479
msgid "Scenario takes place during the night."
msgstr "El escenario ocurre durante la noche."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:493
msgid "The fog in this scenario is very thick."
msgstr "La niebla en este escenario es muy espesa."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=veteran_soldier
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:570
msgid "It's a valley."
msgstr "Es un valle."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:572
msgid "The fog is so thick...I can hardly see anything..."
msgstr "La niebla es tan espesa… apenas puedo ver algo…"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=vampire_leader
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:574
msgid "I sense the arrival of warm blood!"
msgstr "¡Siento la llegada de sangre caliente!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=vampire_leader2
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:576
msgid "We shall feast! Minions, attack!"
msgstr "¡Banquetearemos! ¡Esbirros, ataquen!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=veteran_adept
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:578
msgid "I sense the presence of several vampires!"
msgstr "¡Siento la presencia de varios vampiros!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:580
msgid ""
"We cannot beat them here. We just have to outlast them until they are forced "
"to retreat..."
msgstr ""
"No podemos vencerlos aquí. Solo tenemos que resistir hasta que se vean "
"obligados a retroceder…"

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:583
msgid ""
"This scenario takes place entirely during the night. In this scenario, you "
"will learn one key tactic of playing Aragwaiti: playing defensively and "
"striking when the enemy is most vulnerable. The enemy sides will "
"persistently recruit while you may not be able to. You have to recall "
"Aragwaith Adepts and their advancements to provide healing. If you have any "
"Aragwaith Guards or Pikemen, recall them as well."
msgstr ""
"Este escenario ocurre completamente de noche. Aquí aprenderás una táctica "
"clave para jugar con los Aragwaithi: defender y golpear cuando el enemigo "
"esté más vulnerable. Los bandos enemigos reclutarán sin parar mientras tú "
"tal vez no puedas. Debes reincorporar Adeptas Aragwaithi y sus avances para "
"tener sanación. Si tienes Guardias o Piqueros Aragwaithi, reincorpóralos "
"también."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:585
msgid ""
"Aragwaith units are all <i>neutral</i>, which means they are unaffected by "
"the time of day. Vampire units are either <i>chaotic</i> or <i>neutral</i> "
"which means most of the vampire units will be very strong here. If you see "
"any enemy <i>Blood Apprentices</i> or <i>Blood Hulks</i>, concentrate your "
"attacking power on them to deprive the enemy of using these units."
msgstr ""
"Todas las unidades Aragwaithi son <i>neutrales</i>, por lo que no se ven "
"afectadas por la hora del día. Las unidades Vampiro son <i>caóticas</i> o "
"<i>neutrales</i>, lo que significa que la mayoría serán muy fuertes aquí. Si "
"ves <i>Aprendices de Sangre</i> o <i>Colosos de Sangre</i> enemigos, "
"concentra tu poder de ataque en ellos para privar al enemigo de usarlos."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=unit
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:598
msgid "No, I have shamed the Monarchy!"
msgstr "¡No, he avergonzado a la monarquía!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=unit
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:615
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:632
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:649
msgid "To think I would meet my end like this, it's disappointing."
msgstr "Pensar que encontraría mi fin así… es decepcionante."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:662
msgid ""
"We have defeated them for now. We should rest a bit and proceed southwards."
msgstr "Los derrotamos por ahora. Descansemos un poco y sigamos hacia el sur."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Pyrah
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:689
msgid "I have been recalled this early? What's the situation here?"
msgstr "¿Me reincorporaron tan pronto? ¿Cuál es la situación aquí?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:691
msgid "There are a lot of vampires here."
msgstr "Hay muchos vampiros aquí."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Pyrah
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:693
msgid "I guess I can help out a bit."
msgstr "Supongo que puedo ayudar un poco."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=vampire_leader
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:901
msgid "Argh! Fall back for now. They have resisted our offence."
msgstr "¡Argh! ¡Retírense por ahora! Resistieron nuestro ataque."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=vampire_leader2
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:903
msgid ""
"They seem to be headed where the magic concentration is. I suppose we can "
"let them slip through just this once."
msgstr ""
"Parece que se dirigen hacia donde está la concentración mágica. Supongo que "
"podemos dejarlos pasar solo esta vez."

#. [narrate]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:912
msgid "The vampires withdrew from the valley..."
msgstr "Los vampiros se retiraron del valle…"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:915
msgid "They have retreated... Let's rest up a bit and persist moving south."
msgstr "Se retiraron… Descansemos un poco y sigamos avanzando al sur."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/04_Fogbound_Valley.cfg:917
msgid "Have some scouts patrol the area to avoid being beset by vampires."
msgstr ""
"Que algunos exploradores patrullen la zona para evitar que los vampiros nos "
"rodeen."

#. [scenario], id=05X_Ephemeral_Calm
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:5
msgid "Ephemeral Calm"
msgstr "Calma efímera"

#. [scenario], id=05X_Ephemeral_Calm
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:62
msgid "Go Home"
msgstr "Regresar a casa"

#. [scenario], id=05X_Ephemeral_Calm
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:63
msgid "Advance Further"
msgstr "Avanzar más"

#. [scenario], id=05X_Ephemeral_Calm
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:64
msgid "Light Torches"
msgstr "Encender antorchas"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:83
msgid "Explore the chamber"
msgstr "Explorar la cámara"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:88
msgid "Try to solve the puzzle."
msgstr "Intentar resolver el rompecabezas."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:93
msgid "There is no combat in this scenario."
msgstr "No hay combate en este escenario."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:96
msgid "Hikaru and Soryu have unlimited movement here."
msgstr "Hikaru y Soryu tienen movimiento ilimitado aquí."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:99
msgid "You cannot end your turn."
msgstr "No puedes terminar el turno."

#. [disallow_end_turn]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:112
msgid "You cannot end your turn until you taken an action."
msgstr "No puedes terminar el turno hasta que realices una acción."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:125
msgid "Ah, Hikaru. Thank you for answering my summons."
msgstr "Ah, Hikaru. Gracias por responder a mi llamado."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:127
msgid "Always, Lord Ryuuma!"
msgstr "¡Siempre, señor Ryuuma!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:129
msgid ""
"After the battle, we have searched the castle fortress and found this "
"chamber of sorts. Now, this chamber appears to have two paths: one seems to "
"lead further underground and other is locked by a gate."
msgstr ""
"Después de la batalla, registramos la fortaleza y encontramos esta especie "
"de cámara. Parece tener dos caminos: uno lleva más bajo tierra y el otro "
"está cerrado con una puerta."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:131
msgid ""
"We have tried to force open that second gate but there seems to be some sort "
"of mechanism involved to its opening."
msgstr ""
"Intentamos forzar esa segunda puerta, pero parece que hay algún tipo de "
"mecanismo para abrirla."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:133
msgid ""
"Now, Hikaru. I see that the forces you have brought along have seen their "
"fair share of battle. I do have sufficient forces to progress with the "
"mission but I would appreciate the assistance if you can spare any. Thus, I "
"present you a choice: you can go back home or you can continue onwards with "
"us. No need to rush this. Take your time. Explore a bit, try the mechanism "
"out, or proceed down the tunnel to advance further."
msgstr ""
"Ahora, Hikaru. Veo que las fuerzas que trajiste han pasado por muchas "
"batallas. Yo tengo suficientes tropas para continuar la misión, pero "
"agradecería tu ayuda si puedes brindarla. Te doy una opción: puedes regresar "
"a casa o seguir adelante con nosotros. No hay prisa. Tómate tu tiempo. "
"Explora un poco, prueba el mecanismo o avanza por el túnel."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:135
msgid "Thank you, Lord Ryuuma, we shall make a decision soon."
msgstr "Gracias, señor Ryuuma. Pronto tomaremos una decisión."

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:149
msgid "Hey, wait!"
msgstr "¡Oye, espera!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:151
msgid "Yes?"
msgstr "¿Sí?"

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:153
msgid ""
"If you are going down this path, there is a chamber with some sort of "
"mechanism involving torches."
msgstr ""
"Si van por este camino, hay una cámara con un mecanismo que involucra "
"antorchas."

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:155
msgid ""
"We have been trying for quite some time, but the puzzle seems complex. I "
"wish you luck if you choose to have a go at it yourself."
msgstr ""
"Llevamos un buen rato intentándolo, pero el rompecabezas parece complicado. "
"Te deseo suerte si decides probarlo tú mismo."

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:157
msgid "Lord Ryuuma and the rest seem convinced to take the open path."
msgstr ""
"El señor Ryuuma y los demás parecen decididos a tomar el camino abierto."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:159
msgid "Thanks for letting us know. Let's see if we can solve it some way."
msgstr "Gracias por avisarnos. Veamos si podemos resolverlo de alguna forma."

#. [event], NARRATOR_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:174
msgid "NOT IMPLEMENTED YET"
msgstr "AÚN NO IMPLEMENTADO"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:198
msgid "Let us take this open path!"
msgstr "¡Tomemos este camino abierto!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:200
msgid ""
"Wise choice, Hikaru. We do not know what we will face down there but we "
"shall combat this situation together. Now, onwards!"
msgstr ""
"Buena elección, Hikaru. No sabemos qué enfrentaremos allá abajo, pero lo "
"combatiremos juntos. ¡Ahora, adelante!"

#. [confirm]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:230
msgid "Forfeit Campaign"
msgstr "Abandonar la campaña"

#. [confirm]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:231
msgid "Would you like to abandon this quest and go home?"
msgstr "¿Quieres abandonar esta misión y regresar a casa?"

#. [then], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:238
msgid "We shall be heading home, Lord Ryuuma."
msgstr "Regresaremos a casa, señor Ryuuma."

#. [then], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Ephemeral_Calm.cfg:240
msgid "A safe choice. I wish you a safe journey, my young friends."
msgstr "Una decisión segura. Les deseo un viaje seguro, jóvenes amigos."

#. [scenario], id=05X_Premature_Ending
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05X_Premature_Ending.cfg:6
msgid "Premature Ending"
msgstr "Final prematuro"

#. [scenario], id=05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:6
msgid "The Mage and the Sword"
msgstr "El mago y la espada"

#. [side], type=Great Mage
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:118
msgid "Lady Laraina"
msgstr "Señora Laraina"

#. [spectral_barrier]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:151
msgid "spectral barrier"
msgstr "barrera espectral"

#. [spectral_barrier]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:152
msgid ""
"This unit is manifesting a spectral barrier around itself which makes them "
"nearly invulnerable to almost all damage types. Only electric weapons can "
"penetrate the barrier."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad está manifestando una barrera espectral a su alrededor que la "
"hace casi invulnerable a casi todos los tipos de daño. Solo las armas "
"eléctricas pueden atravesar la barrera."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:270
msgid "Retrieve the Electrifyre"
msgstr "Recuperar la Electryfire"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:277
msgid "Defeat the leader of the Mages and Dwarves"
msgstr "Derrotar al líder de los magos y enanos"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:285
msgid "Find Pyrah's sister"
msgstr "Encontrar a la hermana de Pyrah"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:300
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:198
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:303
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/08A_Enemy_of_My_Enemy.cfg:411
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/09A_Bastion_of_the_Forgotten.cfg:345
msgid "Death of Ryuuma"
msgstr "Muerte de Ryuuma"

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:315
msgid "Try to enter the castle from a side-route."
msgstr "Intenta entrar al castillo por un camino lateral."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:318
msgid "Recall an Aragwaith Enchantress or Sorceress."
msgstr "Reincorpora una Encantadora o una Hechicera Aragwaithi."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:321
msgid "Recall infantry class veterans."
msgstr "Reincorpora veteranos de infantería."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:329
msgid "Only Electrifyre can damage the Mage Lord."
msgstr "Solo la Electryfire puede dañar al Señor Mago."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=veteran_scout
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:524
msgid "Hikaru, the southern trail ends here!"
msgstr "¡Hikaru, el sendero del sur termina aquí!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=veteran_adept
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:526
msgid ""
"There seems to be a castle up ahead. I sense a great magic power inside the "
"castle."
msgstr ""
"Parece que hay un castillo más adelante. Siento un gran poder mágico dentro "
"del castillo."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:528
msgid ""
"We should proceed with caution. We cannot let Electrifyre fall into the "
"wrong hands. It must be returned to its shrine!"
msgstr ""
"Debemos avanzar con cuidado. No podemos permitir que la Electryfire caiga en "
"manos equivocadas. ¡Tiene que volver a su santuario!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:530
msgid "Hello, fellow kinsmen. What brings you here?"
msgstr "Hola, compatriotas. ¿Qué los trae por aquí?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:532
msgid ""
"Our village had been robbed of its relic, and we are here to take it back."
msgstr "Nos robaron la reliquia del pueblo y vinimos a recuperarla."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:534
msgid ""
"Another village has also been plundered for a long-forgotten relic? I was "
"dispatched here from the Royal Capital to investigate and put a stop to "
"these crimes. Let us unite our forces and take down these enemies!"
msgstr ""
"¿Otro pueblo saqueado por una reliquia olvidada hace mucho? Me enviaron "
"desde la capital real para investigar y detener estos crímenes. ¡Unamos "
"nuestras fuerzas y acabemos con estos enemigos!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:536
msgid "Of course!"
msgstr "¡Por supuesto!"

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:539
msgid ""
"Your ally will keep the enemy engaged outside the fortress. What you have to "
"do is form an initial group of veteran units and inflitrate (sneak into) the "
"fortress from one of the side passages."
msgstr ""
"Tu aliado mantendrá al enemigo ocupado fuera de la fortaleza. Lo que debes "
"hacer es formar un grupo inicial de unidades veteranas e infiltrarse (entrar "
"sigilosamente) en la fortaleza por uno de los pasajes laterales."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:541
msgid ""
"You should be able to utilise the tactics on playing Aragwaithi from the "
"previous scenario is this battle such using Guards and Pikemen as damage "
"absorbers or using Adepts or Enchantresses to heal. It is recommended to "
"avoid recalling any flying or scout units as you have to rely on infantry-"
"based and healing units."
msgstr ""
"Puedes usar las tácticas de jugar con Aragwaithi de los escenarios "
"anteriores: usa Guardias y Piqueros como escudos que absorban daño o Adeptas "
"y Encantadoras para sanar. Se recomienda no reincorporar unidades voladoras "
"ni exploradores, ya que dependerás de unidades de infantería y curación."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:549
msgid "Lord Knight, may I know your name?"
msgstr "Señor caballero, ¿puedo saber su nombre?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:551
msgid "I am Ryuuma of House Shimotsuki"
msgstr "Soy Ryuuma de la Casa Shimotsuki."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=veteran_adept
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:553
msgid "House Shimotsuki?!"
msgstr "¡¿Casa Shimotsuki?!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:555
msgid "Are you really..?"
msgstr "¿De verdad eres…?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:557
msgid ""
"Yes, I am the very same. I sometimes do feel my feats in that war are a bit "
"exaggerated though."
msgstr ""
"Sí, soy el mismo. A veces siento que mis hazañas en esa guerra están un poco "
"exageradas."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:564
msgid ""
"Hikaru, try taking your band and infiltrate the castle from a side passage. "
"We shall keep the main enemy force distracted outside."
msgstr ""
"Hikaru, lleva a tu grupo e infíltrate en el castillo por un pasaje lateral. "
"Nosotros mantendremos distraída a la fuerza enemiga principal afuera."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:566
msgid "As you command, Lord Ryuuma!"
msgstr "¡Como ordenes, Señor Ryuuma!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Mage_Leader
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:613
msgid ""
"What do we have here? Have you come to retrieve the relics I requisitioned "
"from you?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué tenemos aquí? ¿Vinieron a recuperar las reliquias que les requisé?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:615
msgid ""
"I do not know why you stole so many relics from the villages and towns, but "
"I shall ensure you return all of them!"
msgstr ""
"No sé por qué robaron tantas reliquias de pueblos y ciudades, ¡pero me "
"encargaré de que las devuelvan todas!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Mage_Leader
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:617
msgid ""
"You're too late, knight. I already sent over most of them. Just a recently "
"stolen one is left."
msgstr ""
"Llegaron tarde, caballero. Ya envié la mayoría. Solo queda una que robamos "
"hace poco."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:619
msgid "That must be the Electrifyre! Quick, we must retrieve it!"
msgstr "¡Esa debe ser la Electryfire! ¡Rápido, tenemos que recuperarla!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:621
msgid "Focus on that mage leader! She must be brought to justice!"
msgstr "¡Concéntrense en esa líder maga! ¡Tiene que rendir cuentas!"

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:624
msgid ""
"If you check the resistances of the enemy leader, you can see that only "
"<i>electric</i> damage attacks can hurt her. Check out the nearby locations, "
"there might be some relic/artifact which can give you this damage type "
"attack."
msgstr ""
"Si revisas las resistencias de la líder enemiga, verás que solo los ataques "
"de daño <i>eléctrico</i> la hieren. Busca en los lugares cercanos: puede "
"haber alguna reliquia o artefacto que dé ese tipo de daño."

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:694
msgid "Hey, wait! I see humans here!"
msgstr "¡Oye, espera! ¡Veo humanos aquí!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:696
msgid "Wow! They must be from the Vale!"
msgstr "¡Vaya! ¡Deben ser habitantes del valle!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:698
msgid "You, there. Why have you aligned with the mages?"
msgstr "Ustedes ahí. ¿Por qué se aliaron con los magos?"

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:704
msgid ""
"We have been ordered by the Leadership to assist the mages in their "
"objectives. You shall not hinder us!"
msgstr ""
"El liderazgo nos ordenó ayudar a los magos en sus objetivos. ¡No nos "
"estorben!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:706
msgid ""
"If you are not a friend, then you are a foe. I suggest you prefer to fight "
"then."
msgstr "Si no son amigos, son enemigos. Les sugiero que prefieran pelear."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:708
msgid ""
"It's a shame they are not friendly. I had many questions I wished to ask."
msgstr ""
"Qué lástima que no sean amistosos. Tenía muchas preguntas que quería "
"hacerles."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:710
msgid ""
"The Valefolk have not been seen since the Argean War, which had occured "
"nearly 200 years ago. It makes me wonder what they are doing here of all "
"places."
msgstr ""
"A los habitantes del valle no se los ha visto desde la Guerra de Argea, hace "
"casi 200 años. Me pregunto qué hacen aquí, de todos los lugares."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:713
msgid ""
"The Valefolk was a sub-faction of humans, like the Aragwaithi. Almost all "
"their units have the <i>liminal</i> alignment. One key observation is that "
"all their advancement trees end at the second level (<b>level 2</b>)."
msgstr ""
"Los habitantes del valle eran una subfacción humana, como los Aragwaithi. "
"Casi todas sus unidades tienen alineación <i>crepuscular</i>. Un detalle "
"importante es que sus líneas de avance terminan en nivel 2."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Mage_Leader
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:734
msgid ""
"Such weapons cannot wound me, fools! Do you think, I, one of the seven mage "
"masters will fall to such pathetic attempts?"
msgstr ""
"¡Esas armas no pueden herirme, idiotas! ¿Creen que yo, una de las siete "
"maestras magas, caeré ante intentos tan patéticos?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:736
msgid ""
"Hmm, she seems to be protected by a magical shield. Maybe we can find "
"something inside the castle that can dissipate it. Quickly, search!"
msgstr ""
"Hmm, parece estar protegida por un escudo mágico. Tal vez encontremos algo "
"dentro del castillo que lo disipe. ¡Rápido, busquen!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:781
msgid ""
"It seems striking her with the Electrifyre distorts the barrier she has been "
"using! This seems to be the key to defeating her!"
msgstr ""
"¡Parece que golpearla con la Electryfire distorsiona la barrera que usa! "
"¡Esta parece ser la clave para derrotarla!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:827
msgid "<i>(launches a ferociously skilled slash)</i> Take that!"
msgstr "<i>(lanza un corte feroz y experto)</i> ¡Toma eso!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Mage_Leader
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:829
msgid "Argh! This weapon... My barrier has been broken!"
msgstr "¡Argh! ¡Esta arma… Mi barrera está rota!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:841
msgid "Well done, everyone!"
msgstr "¡Bien hecho, todos!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Pyrah
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:973
msgid "Hey, wait! I know this place!"
msgstr "¡Oye, espera! ¡Conozco este lugar!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:975
msgid "Have you been here before, Pyrah?"
msgstr "¿Habías estado aquí antes, Pyrah?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Pyrah
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:977
msgid ""
"Well, yeah. This is where I am supposed to be! My sister is somewhere here, "
"probably, taking refuge in a tree somewhere. I should find her."
msgstr ""
"Pues sí. ¡Aquí es donde debo estar! Mi hermana está por aquí, probablemente "
"refugiada en algún árbol. Tengo que encontrarla."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Pyrah
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1014
msgid "Oh, my...this tree..."
msgstr "Oh, Dios… este árbol…"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Pyrah
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1016
msgid "This is it! This is the tree!"
msgstr "¡Este es! ¡Este es el árbol!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1018
msgid "Wait, this is the place you were looking for?"
msgstr "Espera, ¿este es el lugar que buscabas?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1020
msgid "Have you found your sister yet?"
msgstr "¿Ya encontraste a tu hermana?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Pyrah
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1033
msgid "She must be here. She is probably asleep. Let me try calling her!"
msgstr "Debe estar aquí. Seguro está dormida. ¡Déjame llamarla!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Pyrah
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1035
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1037
msgid "Deulara!"
msgstr "¡Deulara!"

#. [event], NAMED_LOYAL_UNIT
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1039
msgid "Deulara"
msgstr "Deulara"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Deulara
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1041
msgid "Ugh. Let me sleep..."
msgstr "Ugh… déjame dormir…"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Deulara
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1043
msgid "Pyrah? Pyrah! You are finally here!"
msgstr "¿Pyrah? ¡Pyrah! ¡Al fin llegaste!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Pyrah
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1045
msgid "Yes! Now, we can resume our jounrey!"
msgstr "¡Sí! ¡Ahora podemos continuar nuestro viaje!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Deulara
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1047
msgid "Yes, we can."
msgstr "Sí, podemos."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Deulara
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1049
msgid "(to Hikaru and the Aragwaithi)"
msgstr "(a Hikaru y los Aragwaithi)"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Deulara
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1049
msgid ""
" Thank you for guiding my sister to me. Before we resume our journey to the "
"sacred grove, I would like to bestow you upon my boon. I hope that makes up "
"for my sister leaving your party."
msgstr ""
"Gracias por guiar a mi hermana hasta mí. Antes de continuar nuestro viaje al "
"bosquecillo sagrado, quiero otorgarles mi bendición. Espero que compense que "
"mi hermana deje su grupo."

#. [item_dialog]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1076
msgid "Staff of the Sorceress"
msgstr "Bastón de la hechicera"

#. [item_dialog]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1078
msgid ""
"Crafted from flawless ivory, the staff gleamed like a polished bone. Its "
"surface, untouched by a single mark, held the chill of a mountain peak. A "
"single, pearlescent orb pulsed at its tip, a heart of magic waiting to be "
"ignited by a destined touch."
msgstr ""
"Tallado en marfil perfecto, el bastón brillaba como hueso pulido. Su "
"superficie, sin una sola marca, guardaba el frío de una cima montañosa. Un "
"único orbe perlado pulsaba en la punta, un corazón de magia esperando ser "
"encendido por un toque destinado."

#. [item_dialog]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1079
msgid ""
"<span fgcolor='grey'><b>Add <i>slows</i> special for ranged attack.</b></"
"span>"
msgstr ""
"<span fgcolor='grey'><b>Agrega la habilidad especial <i>ralentiza</i> al "
"ataque a distancia.</b></span>"

#. [event], NARRATOR_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1125
msgid "Only an Aragwaith Enchantress or Sorceress can equip this artfiact!"
msgstr ""
"¡Solo una Encantadora o Hechicera Aragwaithi puede equipar este artefacto!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Pyrah
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1128
msgid "Farewell! Hope we meet again someday!"
msgstr "¡Adiós! ¡Espero que nos volvamos a ver algún día!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=unit
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1163
msgid "Hey! I found Electrifyre! It's here! Hikaru, come quick! Take it!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oye! ¡Encontré la Electryfire! ¡Está aquí! ¡Hikaru, ven rápido! ¡Tómala!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1177
msgid ""
"Hey, I found a keep! I can rally some more soldiers in this battle from here!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oye, encontré un torreón! ¡Puedo reunir más soldados para esta batalla "
"desde aquí!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Mage_Leader
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1211
msgid "Haha! My teleportation is complete! "
msgstr "¡Ja ja! ¡Mi teletransportación está completa!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1221
msgid "The pesky mage has escaped! Who knows more she has stolen from us!"
msgstr "¡El maldito mago ha escapado! ¡Quién sabe cuánto más nos robó!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/05_The_Mage_and_the_Sword.cfg:1223
msgid "We have failed this mission..."
msgstr "Hemos fracasado en esta misión…"

