msgstr "Akemi"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:471
msgid "Lord Ryuuma, I see an opening up ahead."
msgstr "Señor Ryuuma, veo una abertura más adelante."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:473
msgid "Let me be the vanguard. My shield can block any surprise attacks."
msgstr ""
"Déjame ser la vanguardia. Mi escudo puede bloquear cualquier ataque sorpresa."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:484
msgid "A doorway and its open. Leads to a big chamber."
msgstr "Una puerta abierta. Lleva a una cámara grande."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:497
msgid "Woah! Watch your step, everyone! There is a chasm here."
msgstr "¡Cuidado! ¡Cuidado con el paso! ¡Hay un abismo aquí!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:510
msgid ""
"Another chasm. Might be worthwhile having an eagle rider scout out this "
"chamber a bit."
msgstr ""
"Otro abismo. Valdría la pena que un jinete de águila explore un poco esta "
"cámara."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:521
msgid ""
"Excellent. Two keeps. We can rally our forces here if the need arises. Take "
"the other keep, Hikaru."
msgstr ""
"Excelente. Dos torreones. Podemos reunir nuestras fuerzas aquí si es "
"necesario. Toma el otro torreón, Hikaru."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:530
msgid "I am in position."
msgstr "Estoy en posición."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:539
msgid "Okay, we are in position! Let's rally our troops and press forward..."
msgstr "¡Bien, estamos en posición! ¡Reunamos nuestras tropas y avancemos…"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:562
msgid "What's happening? The gates have closed!"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa? ¡Las puertas se cerraron!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryi
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:564
msgid "We cannot turn back now!"
msgstr "¡Ya no podemos retroceder!"

#. [then], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Eikichi
#. [else], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Eikichi
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:571
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:574
msgid "Did we trigger a trap or something?"
msgstr "¿Activamos una trampa o algo?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:578
msgid "Stand firm, everyone!"
msgstr "¡Manténganse firmes, todos!"

#. [unit], id=Xulthar, type=Jinn
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:602
msgid "Xul'thar"
msgstr "Xul'thar"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Xulthar
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:620
msgid "Welcome, exalted guests! I am Xul'thar, an entity from a bygone era."
msgstr ""
"¡Bienvenidos, ilustres invitados! Soy Xul'thar, una entidad de una era "
"olvidada."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:622
msgid ""
"I am Ryuuma Shimotsuki of the Aragwaithi and these are brave soldiers and "
"mages in my regiment. We seek passage further into the depths."
msgstr ""
"Soy Ryuuma Shimotsuki de los aragwaithi y estos son valientes soldados y "
"magos de mi regimiento. Buscamos paso hacia las profundidades."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Xulthar
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:624
msgid "I am thrilled to make your acquaintance. Now, we shall begin!"
msgstr "Me emociona conocerlos. ¡Ahora, comenzaremos!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:626
msgid "What? What do you mean by that?"
msgstr "¿Qué? ¿Qué quieres decir con eso?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Xulthar
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:628
msgid ""
"Is not it obvious? You all carelessly step into my realm and except to walk "
"out of here unscathed? Hardly!"
msgstr ""
"¿No es obvio? Todos entraron descuidadamente en mi dominio y esperan salir "
"ilesos. ¡Difícil!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Xulthar
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:630
msgid ""
"The objective is simple. You will battle and face my minions and make some "
"paltry attempt to vanquish me, where as, I shall watch your endeavours and "
"eventual failure. Then, I am entertained and will reset the chamber to "
"repeat the cycle."
msgstr ""
"El objetivo es simple. Lucharán contra mis esbirros e intentarán vencerme, "
"mientras yo observo sus esfuerzos y su fracaso final. Luego, me entretengo y "
"reinicio la cámara para repetir el ciclo."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Xulthar
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:632
msgid ""
"Does that not sound entertaining? It's different every time and I enjoy it "
"every time!"
msgstr "¿No suena entretenido? Cada vez es diferente y lo disfruto cada vez."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:634
msgid "Oh, no! It's a crazed Jinn!"
msgstr "¡Oh, no! ¡Es un jinn loco!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:636
msgid ""
"I refuse to accept such a fate. Maybe we can make a different outcome. We "
"have to try!"
msgstr ""
"Me niego a aceptar ese destino. Tal vez podamos cambiar el resultado. "
"¡Tenemos que intentarlo!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:638
msgid ""
"Hikaru speaks wisdom. We shall not succumb to the odds regardless of how "
"overwhelming they might be. Now, prepare for battle!"
msgstr ""
"Hikaru habla con sabiduría. No nos rendiremos sin importar lo abrumadoras "
"que sean las probabilidades. ¡Ahora, prepárense para la batalla!"

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:640
msgid ""
"There is no way to attack the Jinn directly. You must explore the chamber "
"and discover some alternate way to defeat the Jinn."
msgstr ""
"No hay forma de atacar directamente al jinn. Deben explorar la cámara y "
"descubrir alguna otra manera de derrotarlo."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:648
msgid ""
"Foes come at us from all directions. At least we have keeps to rally our "
"soldiers from."
msgstr ""
"Los enemigos nos atacan desde todas partes. Al menos tenemos torreones para "
"reunir a nuestros soldados."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Xulthar
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:650
msgid "You forget one thing...I control everything in this space!"
msgstr "Olvidan una cosa… ¡yo controlo todo en este espacio!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Xulthar
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:652
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1208
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1236
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1256
msgid "Chants indiscernable black speech"
msgstr "Canta en lengua negra ininteligible"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:672
msgid "Oh, no! The keeps!"
msgstr "¡Oh, no! ¡Los torreones!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:674
msgid ""
"Do not fret! We can win this with whatever forces we have on the field "
"currently!"
msgstr ""
"¡No se preocupen! ¡Podemos ganar esto con las fuerzas que tenemos en el "
"campo ahora!"

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:676
msgid ""
"Your keeps are now gone and you must win with the units you have on the map "
"currently."
msgstr ""
"Ya no tienes torreones y debes ganar con las unidades que tienes actualmente "
"en el mapa."

#. [then], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Xulthar
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:821
msgid "Ouch! That hurts!"
msgstr "¡Auch! ¡Eso duele!"

#. [then], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:823
msgid "Destroying that pillar caused the Jinn to take damage!"
msgstr "¡Destruir ese pilar hizo daño al jinn!"

#. [then], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:825
msgid "Maybe we have to find and destroy more of these obelisks!"
msgstr "¡Tal vez tengamos que encontrar y destruir más de estos obeliscos!"

#. [then], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Xulthar
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:848
msgid "Curses on you!"
msgstr "¡Malditos sean!"

#. [then], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:850
msgid ""
"Destroying a second pillar brought the Jinn's lifepoints to half! Just two "
"more and we can win this!"
msgstr ""
"¡Destruir un segundo pilar bajó a la mitad la vida del jinn! ¡Solo faltan "
"dos más y ganamos!"

#. [then], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Xulthar
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:873
msgid "Ouch! That hurts a lot!"
msgstr "¡Auch! ¡Eso duele mucho!"

#. [then], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:875
msgid "That's three! One more and we can defeat this Jinn!"
msgstr "¡Son tres! ¡Uno más y derrotamos a este jinn!"

#. [then], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Xulthar
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:898
msgid "I cannot believe this!"
msgstr "¡No puedo creer esto!"

#. [then], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:900
msgid "All four obelisks have been destroyed! Great work, everyone!"
msgstr "¡Los cuatro obeliscos han sido destruidos! ¡Gran trabajo, todos!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:926
msgid "Did we win?"
msgstr "¿Ganamos?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:956
msgid "The entrance gates have opened!"
msgstr "¡Las puertas de entrada se abrieron!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:994
msgid ""
"The jinn has been suppresed. We should resume our advance right away. It "
"would be gravely exhausting if he came back to harass us once again."
msgstr ""
"El jinn ha sido suprimido. Debemos reanudar el avance de inmediato. Sería "
"muy agotador si vuelve a molestarnos otra vez."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:996
msgid "I wonder who that jinn was? He seemed really powerful."
msgstr "Me pregunto quién era ese jinn. Parecía realmente poderoso."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:998
msgid ""
"Strong jinn like him existed during the First Elemental War. All of them "
"were once created by the Dark One. Once he was sealed away, the Jinn were "
"freed from servitude and did as they pleased. This one probably made this "
"cavern and decided to play a death game with whoever showed up."
msgstr ""
"Jinns poderosos como él existieron durante la Primera Guerra Elemental. "
"Todos fueron creados por el Oscuro. Cuando fue sellado, los jinns quedaron "
"libres y hicieron lo que quisieron. Este probablemente creó esta caverna y "
"decidió jugar a un juego mortal con quien apareciera."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1000
msgid "I hope we gave the jinn his final rest then."
msgstr "Espero que le hayamos dado su descanso final."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1002
msgid "I hope so as well. Now, we must proceed further."
msgstr "Eso espero también. Ahora debemos seguir adelante."

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1036
msgid ""
"Hey, I can see that we can effectively navigate this place with our eagles!"
msgstr "¡Oye, veo que podemos movernos bien por aquí con nuestras águilas!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1038
msgid ""
"Excellent thinking! We can have eagle riders scout and identify any "
"potential methods of suppressing the Jinn!"
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente idea! ¡Los jinetes de águila pueden explorar y encontrar formas "
"de suprimir al jinn!"

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1043
msgid "Leave it to us, Lord Ryuuma!"
msgstr "¡Déjenoslo a nosotros, señor Ryuuma!"

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1046
msgid ""
"<i>Eagle Riders</i> and <i>Eagle Masters</i> will be pivotable for this "
"scenario. You may recruit/recall more but it is best if you keep your army "
"balanced."
msgstr ""
"Los <i>jinetes de águila</i> y <i>maestros de águila</i> serán clave en este "
"escenario. Puedes reclutar o reincorporar más, pero es mejor mantener el "
"ejército equilibrado."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1048
msgid ""
"This scenario might be unwinnable if you end up losing all your eagle riders/"
"masters before completing their specific goal. In the unwinnable case, it is "
"advised to load a previous save and try again."
msgstr ""
"Este escenario puede volverse impasable si pierdes todos tus jinetes y "
"maestros de águila antes de cumplir su objetivo específico. En ese caso, se "
"recomienda cargar una partida guardada anterior e intentarlo de nuevo."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1057
msgid ""
"In the next few scenarios and the following, you can control the movements "
"of your allied leader, Ryuuma. If you right-click on Ryuuma, you can see "
"that you can order him to stay on his current hex. If you have done, you can "
"right-click again and disable that command."
msgstr ""
"En los próximos escenarios puedes controlar los movimientos de tu líder "
"aliado, Ryuuma. Si haces clic derecho sobre Ryuuma, verás que puedes "
"ordenarle quedarse en su casilla actual. Para cancelar la orden, haz clic "
"derecho otra vez."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1059
msgid ""
"On any other reachable hex, you can tell Ryuuma to move there as well via "
"right-clicking. You can also cancel that movement order via right-clicking "
"again. When selecting a hex for Ryuuma to moveto, always pick one within his "
"movement range. Otherwise, he will not move."
msgstr ""
"En cualquier otra casilla alcanzable, puedes ordenarle a Ryuuma que se mueva "
"allí con clic derecho. Puedes cancelar esa orden con otro clic derecho. Al "
"elegir una casilla para Ryuuma, siempre elige una dentro de su rango de "
"movimiento; de lo contrario, no se moverá."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1061
msgid ""
"Ryuuma will attack anything he gets adjacent too, but remember well that he "
"is a powerful tank unit (a unit with strong defense and damage reduction) so "
"strategically position him to prevent enemy progression."
msgstr ""
"Ryuuma atacará cualquier cosa que se le acerque, pero recuerda que es una "
"unidad tanque poderosa (con gran defensa y reducción de daño), así que "
"posiciona estratégicamente para bloquear el avance enemigo."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1063
msgid ""
"The other units of Ryuuma side will follow him and attack enemies in the "
"surrounding area of Ryuuma."
msgstr ""
"Las demás unidades del bando de Ryuuma lo seguirán y atacarán a los enemigos "
"cerca de él."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=second_unit
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1084
msgid "Hey, I see this small tower, and it's summoning things!"
msgstr "¡Oye, veo esta torre pequeña y está invocando cosas!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1086
msgid "Those might be the jinn's conduits! Destroy them!"
msgstr "¡Esos deben ser los conductos del jinn! ¡Destrúyanlos!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1088
msgid "You heard him! Let's go!"
msgstr "¡Lo oyeron! ¡Vamos!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1106
msgid "Look! The Valefolk are here!"
msgstr "¡Miren! ¡Los habitantes del valle están aquí!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1108
msgid "They appear to be trapped here as well!"
msgstr "¡También parecen estar atrapados aquí!"

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1110
msgid "The aragwaithi are here?! Does that mean the Mage Lord was defeated?"
msgstr ""
"¿¡Los aragwaithi están aquí!? ¿Eso significa que derrotaron a la señora maga?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1112
msgid ""
"It seems the mage lord's magic had suppressed the Jinn this whole time and "
"without her, the Jinn is now free to enact his games."
msgstr ""
"Parece que la magia de la señora maga mantenía suprimido al jinn todo este "
"tiempo y sin ella, ahora el jinn es libre de jugar sus juegos."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=second_unit
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1127
msgid "There are saurians here!"
msgstr "¡Hay saurios aquí!"

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1129
msgid "Ah, more treasure thieves! Defend the treasure!"
msgstr "¡Ah, más ladrones de tesoros! ¡Defiendan el tesoro!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1131
msgid ""
"It seems they have piled a considerable portion of gold there. It would be "
"nice if you requistioned it for ourselves."
msgstr ""
"Parece que amontonaron una buena cantidad de oro ahí. Sería bueno requisarlo "
"para nosotros."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1146
msgid ""
"Undead...they have not been seen since the end of the First Elemental War!"
msgstr ""
"No muertos… ¡no se los veía desde el final de la Primera Guerra Elemental!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hirgon
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1148
msgid "You can attack us all you want but we shall never yield, damned jinn!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pueden atacarnos todo lo que quieran, pero nunca nos rendiremos, maldito "
"jinn!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1150
msgid ""
"They may be undead but they seem to be opposing the Jinn as well. We might "
"be able to use this to our advantage."
msgstr ""
"Pueden ser no muertos, pero también se oponen al jinn. Tal vez podamos usar "
"eso a nuestro favor."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Xulthar
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1206
msgid "Still standing? It does not matter. I shall now end you myself!"
msgstr "¿Todavía de pie? No importa. ¡Ahora los acabaré yo mismo!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Xulthar
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1224
msgid ""
"I guess I go back to my slumber and wait for the next set of fools to enter "
"my domain..."
msgstr ""
"Supongo que vuelvo a dormir y espero al próximo grupo de tontos que entre en "
"mi dominio…"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Xulthar
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1234
msgid "This is taking too long!"
msgstr "¡Esto está tardando demasiado!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1246
msgid "He has inflicted a slowing curse on us!"
msgstr "¡Nos lanzó una maldición de ralentización!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Xulthar
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1254
msgid "Perhaps I was being too lenient..."
msgstr "Tal vez fui demasiado indulgente…"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1269
msgid "This is even more terrible than the last one!"
msgstr "¡Esto es aún peor que el anterior!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/06A_Forsaken_Hall.cfg:1271
msgid "We must make haste and defeat him or he might execute us for good!"
msgstr "¡Debemos apresurarnos y derrotarlo o nos matará de verdad!"

#. [scenario], id=07A_Realm_of_Stings
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:5
msgid "Realm of Stings"
msgstr "Reino de los aguijones"

#. [side]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:85
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:196
msgid "Scorpions"
msgstr "Escorpiones"

#. [side]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:101
msgid "Crabs"
msgstr "Cangrejos"

#. [side]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:148
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/08A_Enemy_of_My_Enemy.cfg:82
msgid "Shrooms"
msgstr "Hongos"

#. [side]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:164
msgid "Serpents"
msgstr "Serpientes"

#. [side]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:180
msgid "Mud Crawlers"
msgstr "Reptadores de barro"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:297
msgid "Move Ryuuma to the eastern edge of the map"
msgstr "Llevar a Ryuuma al borde este del mapa"

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:322
msgid "Avoid killing too many scorpions."
msgstr "Evita matar demasiados escorpiones."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:325
msgid "Recall only non-scout units."
msgstr "Reincorpora solo unidades que no sean exploradores."

#. [note]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:328
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/08A_Enemy_of_My_Enemy.cfg:431
msgid "The Shrooms are invulnerable."
msgstr "Los hongos son invulnerables."

#. [event], NAMED_UNIT
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:409
msgid "Oko"
msgstr "Oko"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:517
msgid "I see the entrance to another huge cavern!"
msgstr "¡Veo la entrada a otra enorme caverna!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:558
msgid "I see a lot of movement ahead!"
msgstr "¡Veo mucho movimiento más adelante!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:560
msgid "We better make camp here to rally the soldiers."
msgstr "Mejor acampemos aquí para reunir a los soldados."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:567
msgid ""
"Ah, I see. It's an underground mushroom forest! It is growing over a "
"quagmire. I wonder what manner of interesting fauna and flora we might see "
"while traversing through here."
msgstr ""
"Ah, ya veo. ¡Es un bosque subterráneo de hongos! Crece sobre un pantano. Me "
"pregunto qué tipo de fauna y flora interesante encontraremos al atravesarlo."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:569
msgid "Lord Ryuuma, should we try an exploration here?"
msgstr "Señor Ryuuma, ¿deberíamos explorar por aquí?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:571
msgid ""
"I would like to do so as well however, time is of the essence. We must press "
"on."
msgstr ""
"A mí también me gustaría, pero el tiempo apremia. Debemos seguir adelante."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:573
msgid ""
"I shall rally my troops right away and begin preparations to mobilise. You "
"can start at your pace and maybe explore the area a bit. Who knows what we "
"may find."
msgstr ""
"Reuniré a mis tropas de inmediato y comenzaré los preparativos para avanzar. "
"Ustedes pueden empezar a su ritmo y tal vez explorar un poco la zona. Quién "
"sabe qué encontraremos."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:596
msgid ""
"There is a lot of rough terrain here. I hope I can recall the right veterans "
"for this exploration."
msgstr ""
"Hay mucho terreno difícil aquí. Espero reincorporar a los veteranos "
"adecuados para esta exploración."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:599
msgid ""
"The majority of terrain in this map is mushrooms, caves and swamp. In cases "
"such as this, recalling Aragwaith Scouts, Aragwaith Eagle Riders and their "
"advancements should be avoided. Instead, focus on recalling foot-based "
"units.Recalling an additional healer to complement Soryu can be a valuable "
"decision to make in this scenario."
msgstr ""
"La mayor parte del terreno en este mapa son hongos, cuevas y pantano. En "
"casos como este, evita reincorporar exploradores aragwaithi, jinetes de "
"águila aragwaithi y sus avances. En su lugar, enfócate en reincorporar "
"unidades de infantería. Reincorporar un sanador adicional para complementar "
"a Soryu puede ser una decisión valiosa en este escenario."

#. [event], DISPLAY_HINT_MESSAGE
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:609
msgid ""
"Enemies will spawn at set intervals randomly on the map. You should always "
"position your units defensively when ending a turn. Your objective is "
"escorting Ryuuma to the eastern edge of the map and you should prioritise "
"that."
msgstr ""
"Los enemigos aparecerán a intervalos fijos de forma aleatoria en el mapa. "
"Siempre debes posicionar tus unidades de forma defensiva al terminar el "
"turno. Tu objetivo es escoltar a Ryuuma hasta el borde este del mapa y debes "
"priorizar eso."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:682
msgid "What is going on?"
msgstr "¿Qué está pasando?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:687
msgid "The whole place is shaking uncontrollably."
msgstr "Todo el lugar tiembla sin control."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:689
msgid "Something has been awoken..."
msgstr "Algo ha despertado…"

#. [unit], id=Akrabna, type=Queen Scorpion
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:698
msgid "Akrabna"
msgstr "Akrabna"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:814
msgid "Fascinating...a matriach among the scorpions! A rare creature!"
msgstr "¡Fascinante… una matriarca entre los escorpiones! ¡Una criatura rara!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:816
msgid ""
"Rare and looks very vicous. I think we have been perceived as intruders in "
"her territory."
msgstr ""
"Rara y parece muy feroz. Creo que nos han percibido como intrusos en su "
"territorio."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:818
msgid ""
"Tread past her if you can. If confrontation is inevitable, we must be ready "
"for battle."
msgstr ""
"Pasa de largo si puedes. Si el enfrentamiento es inevitable, debemos estar "
"listos para la batalla."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:939
msgid ""
"This path leads us out of here. Let us leave immediately. I do not see these "
"scorpions retreating anytime soon."
msgstr ""
"Este camino nos saca de aquí. Vámonos de inmediato. No veo a estos "
"escorpiones retirándose pronto."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:961
msgid "We have wasted too much time here!"
msgstr "¡Hemos perdido demasiado tiempo aquí!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:963
msgid "We are surrounded by scorpions! I do not see any end to this!"
msgstr "¡Estamos rodeados de escorpiones! ¡No veo fin a esto!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:980
msgid ""
"The abundance of mushrooms here make this perfect location for a breeding "
"ground. A breeding ground for many species of scorpion."
msgstr ""
"La abundancia de hongos hace de este lugar un sitio perfecto para criar. Un "
"criadero para muchas especies de escorpión."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:982
msgid ""
"We should form a defensive formation and avoid getting stung by the scorpion "
"venom while tread through this place."
msgstr ""
"Deberíamos formar una formación defensiva y evitar que nos piquen con el "
"veneno de los escorpiones mientras atravesamos este lugar."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:997
msgid "Hey, it's more of those giant crab creatures again!"
msgstr "¡Oye, son más de esas criaturas cangrejo gigantes otra vez!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:999
msgid ""
"These look more wild than the domesticated ones we saw at the fortress. "
"Where are they coming from?"
msgstr ""
"Estos parecen más salvajes que los domesticados que vimos en la fortaleza. "
"¿De dónde salen?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:1001
msgid ""
"We should avoid engaging them as they seem to be interesting in brawling "
"with the scorpions."
msgstr ""
"Deberíamos evitar enfrentarlos, ya que parecen interesados en pelear con los "
"escorpiones."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:1016
msgid "Saurians are here too? They might be guarding their treasure hoard."
msgstr "¿También hay saurios aquí? Tal vez estén custodiando su tesoro."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:1018
msgid ""
"I would conflicting with them if I can. However, the chance of getting a "
"considerable amount of treasure does sound tempting."
msgstr ""
"Evitaría enfrentarlos si puedo. Sin embargo, la posibilidad de obtener una "
"buena cantidad de tesoro suena tentadora."

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:1033
msgid "It's the invaders! They are coming for the fortress! Stop them here!"
msgstr "¡Son los invasores! ¡Vienen por la fortaleza! ¡Deténganlos aquí!"

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:1040
msgid "Fortress? What fortress?"
msgstr "¿Fortaleza? ¿Qué fortaleza?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:1055
msgid ""
"Avoid striking the giantic mushroom creatures. I think they will release the "
"spores on their surface when hit so it will be bad for us if that happens."
msgstr ""
"Evita golpear a las criaturas hongo gigantes. Creo que liberarán las esporas "
"de su superficie al ser golpeadas y eso sería malo para nosotros."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:1067
msgid "It may have been the last of its kind..."
msgstr "Tal vez fue el último de su especie…"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07A_Realm_of_Stings.cfg:1069
msgid "It does not sound triumphant when you word it like that."
msgstr "No suena triunfal cuando lo dices así."

#. [scenario], id=07B_Lake_in_the_Depths
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07B_Lake_in_the_Depths.cfg:5
msgid "Lake in the Depths"
msgstr "Lago en las profundidades"

#. [scenario], id=07X_A_New_Ally
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:5
msgid "A New Ally"
msgstr "Un nuevo aliado"

#. [side]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:98
msgid "team_name^Windsong"
msgstr "Hijas del Viento"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:124
msgid "These caverns seem to be getting darker and more ominous."
msgstr "Estas cavernas se ven cada vez más oscuras y siniestras."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:125
msgid "Aye. However, we must press on."
msgstr "Sí. Sin embargo, debemos seguir adelante."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:137
msgid "I see what appears to be a crossroads ahead."
msgstr "Veo lo que parece un cruce más adelante."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:207
msgid "Which way do we go now?"
msgstr "¿Por dónde vamos ahora?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:209
msgid "Food and water are running a bit low right now."
msgstr "La comida y el agua están un poco escasas ahora."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:211
msgid ""
"I believe we should pitch camp here. I can see most of us are exhausted "
"right now and we should all get some rest."
msgstr ""
"Creo que deberíamos acampar aquí. Veo que la mayoría está agotada y todos "
"necesitamos descansar."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:301
msgid ""
"How long do you think has it been since we descended underground, Soryu?"
msgstr "¿Cuánto crees que ha pasado desde que bajamos al subsuelo, Soryu?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:303
msgid "I would say a week or so."
msgstr "Diría que una semana más o menos."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:305
msgid ""
"A campfire such as this reminds of the time when I was stationed near the "
"southern border. The war waged on and we fought on."
msgstr ""
"Una fogata como esta me recuerda la época en que estuve estacionado cerca de "
"la frontera sur. La guerra continuaba y nosotros seguíamos luchando."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:307
msgid ""
"Would you tell us a tale from your adventures? We read about them but to "
"hear them from the very source. Now, that would be grand."
msgstr ""
"¿Nos contarías una historia de sus aventuras? Leímos sobre ellas, pero "
"escucharlas de la fuente misma sería genial."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:309
msgid "Why certainly! There was..."
msgstr "¡Claro que sí! Hubo una vez…"

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:315
msgid "Lord Ryuuma, I see movement in the darkness!"
msgstr "¡Señor Ryuuma, veo movimiento en la oscuridad!"

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:319
msgid "I am seeing a lot of pairs of bluish eyes in the darkness ahead!"
msgstr "¡Veo muchos pares de ojos azulados en la oscuridad adelante!"

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:323
msgid "Same here."
msgstr "Yo también."

#. [event], UNIT_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:327
msgid "Same from here as well."
msgstr "Igual desde aquí."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:329
msgid "Quick, take defensive..."
msgstr "¡Rápido, posiciones defensivas…"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:357
msgid "Oh, no! We are surrounded!"
msgstr "¡Oh, no! ¡Estamos rodeados!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:359
msgid "Hold fast! Close ranks!"
msgstr "¡Manténganse firmes! ¡Cierren filas!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:361
msgid "This is going to be an ugly fight..."
msgstr "Esto va a ser una pelea fea…"

#. [unit], id=Yuki, type=Prophetess
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:367
msgid "Yuki"
msgstr "Yuki"

#. [unit], id=Marin, type=Stormbringer
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:380
msgid "Marin"
msgstr "Marin"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Yuki
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:392
msgid "Wait! They are not your enemy!"
msgstr "¡Espera! ¡No son sus enemigos!"

#. [unit], id=Erilyn, type=Elthare
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:397
msgid "Erilyn"
msgstr "Erilyn"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Erilyn
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:416
msgid "They are not? But...they are humans!"
msgstr "¿No lo son? ¡Pero… son humanos!"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Marin
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:418
msgid ""
"That is true. However, if you look closer, you see they are all silver "
"golden-haired and have green eyes. The ones you have a bitter feud with have "
"black hair and always wear armor."
msgstr ""
"Es cierto. Pero si miras más de cerca, verás que todos tienen cabello "
"plateado dorado y ojos verdes. Los que tienen una enemistad amarga contigo "
"tienen cabello negro y siempre usan armadura."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Yuki
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:420
msgid "They are aragwaithi."
msgstr "Son aragwaithi."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Yuki
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:422
msgid "Tell me, Aragwaithi. What are you doing here?"
msgstr "Dime, aragwaithi. ¿Qué hacen aquí?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Marin
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:424
msgid "Pretty far from home, isn't it?"
msgstr "Bastante lejos de casa, ¿no?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:426
msgid ""
"Windsong. I never would have guessed we would run into you here out of all "
"places. I should be asking the same question."
msgstr ""
"Hijas del Viento. Nunca imaginé que nos encontraríamos aquí de todos los "
"lugares. Debería hacerte la misma pregunta."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:428
msgid ""
"To answer your question: we are on a mission to stop the valefolk from "
"raiding aragwaithi territory ever again. They have raided far too many of "
"our villages."
msgstr ""
"Para responder tu pregunta: estamos en una misión para evitar que los "
"habitantes del valle vuelvan a saquear territorio aragwaithi. Han saqueado "
"demasiados de nuestros pueblos."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Yuki
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:430
msgid ""
"We, Windsong, are on a clandestine mission as well. These deep elves, the "
"followers of Shassagoth, are our allies. They are escorting us where we need "
"to go."
msgstr ""
"Nosotras, Hijas del Viento, también estamos en una misión secreta. Estos "
"elfos profundos, seguidores de Shassagoth, son nuestros aliados. Nos "
"escoltan a donde necesitamos ir."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Marin
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:432
msgid ""
"Lately, they have clashed with the valefolk and their dwarven allies in the "
"depths of Irdya."
msgstr ""
"Últimamente han chocado con los habitantes del valle y sus aliados enanos en "
"las profundidades de Irdya."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Erilyn
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:440
msgid "So, we shall let them live?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿los dejaremos vivir?"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Marin
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:442
msgid ""
"Yes, and maybe they can even help you out. You both are fighting the "
"valefolk and their allies. So, it does make sense to establish a temporary "
"alliance."
msgstr ""
"Sí, y tal vez hasta puedan ayudarlos. Ambos luchan contra los habitantes del "
"valle y sus aliados. Tiene sentido establecer una alianza temporal."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Yuki
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:444
msgid ""
"As much as I would like to converse with your sorceresses over tea here, we "
"must be going. It was nice to meet you, aragwaithi. We shall be on our way "
"now. The urgency demands it."
msgstr ""
"Por más que quisiera charlar con sus hechiceras tomando té, debemos irnos. "
"Fue un gusto conocerlos, aragwaithi. Nos vamos. La urgencia lo exige."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Erilyn
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:446
msgid ""
"I have sent a scout back to the main group preparing to fight near by. One "
"of their leaders will come and tell you the details. I suggest you wait and "
"rest till then."
msgstr ""
"Envié un explorador al grupo principal que se prepara para pelear cerca. Uno "
"de sus líderes vendrá a explicarles los detalles. Sugiero que esperen y "
"descansen hasta entonces."

#. [event], NARRATOR_MSG
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:454
msgid ""
"The Windsong and their deep elven allies disengaged and resumed their "
"southern trek. At a glance, Hikaru could interprete that the Windsong, as "
"few as they were, were battle-hardened and their countenances revealed the "
"significane of their mission. Like them, the aragwaithi were on a similar "
"mission."
msgstr ""
"Las Hijas del Viento y sus aliados elfos profundos se retiraron y reanudaron "
"su marcha hacia el sur. De un vistazo, Hikaru pudo notar que las Hijas del "
"Viento, aunque pocas, estaban curtidas en batalla y sus rostros revelaban la "
"importancia de su misión. Al igual que ellas, los aragwaithi estaban en una "
"misión similar."

#. [alert]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:458
msgid "Note from Lord-Knightmare"
msgstr "Nota de Lord-Knightmare"

#. [alert]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:459
msgid ""
"If you are curious to know who Yuki, Marin, and Erilyn are and what their "
"mission is, please play <i>Blackfire</i>, a campaign that takes around as "
"the same time as this one."
msgstr ""
"Si tienes curiosidad por saber quiénes son Yuki, Marin y Erilyn y cuál es su "
"misión, por favor juega <i>Blackfire</i>, una campaña que dura "
"aproximadamente lo mismo que esta."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Soryu
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:463
msgid "That was...intense."
msgstr "Eso fue… intenso."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:465
msgid "(sheathing back swords)"
msgstr "(envainando las espadas)"

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:465
msgid "Indeed, I felt like we were goners."
msgstr "Sí, sentí que estábamos perdidos."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Ryuuma
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:467
msgid ""
"The aragwaithi and windsong have fought alongside each other during the "
"First Elemental War. They are remember and so do we. The windsong have saved "
"us today. We now have time to resume our rest."
msgstr ""
"Los aragwaithi y las Hijas del Viento lucharon juntos durante la Primera "
"Guerra Elemental. Ellos nos recuerdan y nosotros también. Las Hijas del "
"Viento nos salvaron hoy. Ahora tenemos tiempo para descansar."

#. [event], SIMPLE_MSG, speaker=Hikaru
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/07X_A_New_Ally.cfg:469
msgid "Let us rest as much as we can. Another battle does not seem faraway."
msgstr "Descansemos todo lo que podamos. Otra batalla no parece estar lejos."

#. [scenario], id=08A_Enemy_of_My_Enemy
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/08A_Enemy_of_My_Enemy.cfg:5
msgid "Enemy of My Enemy"
msgstr "El enemigo de mi enemigo"

#. [side]
#: Electrifyre/scenarios/08A_Enemy_of_My_Enemy.cfg:123
