msgstr "Caravana de suministros"

#. [unit_type], id=Supply Caravan, race=mechanical
#: Electrifyre/units/mechanical/Supply_Caravan.cfg:27
msgid ""
"Caravans are used to carry gold or supplies long distances. Because of the "
"immense weight of the cargo this caravan carries, it is not nimble, but the "
"driver can still try to drive off attackers with his whip."
msgstr ""
"Las caravanas se usan para transportar oro o suministros a largas "
"distancias. Debido al peso inmenso de la carga que lleva esta caravana, no "
"es ágil, pero el conductor aún puede intentar ahuyentar a los atacantes con "
"su látigo."

#. [special_note]
#: Electrifyre/units/mechanical/Supply_Caravan.cfg:30
msgid ""
"The length of this unit’s improvised weapon allows it to strike first in "
"defensive melee, but it cannot use it to attack."
msgstr ""
"La longitud del arma improvisada de esta unidad le permite golpear primero "
"en combate cuerpo a cuerpo defensivo, pero no puede usarla para atacar."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: Electrifyre/units/mechanical/Supply_Caravan.cfg:38
msgid "whip"
msgstr "látigo"

#. [firststrike]
#: Electrifyre/units/mechanical/Supply_Caravan.cfg:47
msgid "deterrent strike"
msgstr "golpe disuasorio"

#. [firststrike]
#: Electrifyre/units/mechanical/Supply_Caravan.cfg:48
msgid ""
"This unit always strikes first with this attack if they are defending, but "
"cannot attack with it at all."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad siempre golpea primero con este ataque si está defendiendo, pero "
"no puede atacar con él en absoluto."

#. [unit_type], id=Abomination, race=monster
#: Electrifyre/units/monsters/Abomination.cfg:5
msgid "Abomination"
msgstr "Abominación"

#. [unit_type], id=Abomination, race=monster
#: Electrifyre/units/monsters/Abomination.cfg:19
msgid ""
"However they came into existence, they appear to be highly sensitive to "
"light and avoid leaving the safety of their dark caverns."
msgstr ""
"Sea como fuere que llegaron a existir, parecen ser muy sensibles a la luz y "
"evitan abandonar la seguridad de sus cavernas oscuras."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
